068" end="14.297">the</span> <span begin="14.297" end="14.544">ve</span><span begin="14.544" end="14.687">ry</span> <span begin="14.794" end="15.024">fir</span><span begin="15.024" end="15.177">st</span> <span begin="15.281" end="16.241">night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我想念你 宛如初见的那个夜晚</span></p><p begin="17.002" end="18.344" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="17.002" end="17.223">And</span> <span begin="17.223" end="17.540">so</span> <span begin="17.540" end="17.768">it</span> <span begin="17.768" end="18.186">goe</span><span begin="18.186" end="18.344">s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">事情就是这样</span></p><p begin="18.523" end="20.273" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="18.523" end="18.756">Every</span> <span begin="18.756" end="18.991">wee</span><span begin="18.991" end="19.225">kend,</span> <span begin="19.256" end="19.444">thi</span><span begin="19.444" end="19.507">s</span> <span begin="19.507" end="19.737">same</span> <span begin="19.737" end="20.059">par</span><span begin="20.059" end="20.273">ty</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">每个周末 还是同样的派对</span></p><p begin="20.461" end="24.215" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="20.461" end="20.737">I</span> <span begin="20.737" end="21.025">nev</span><span begin="21.025" end="21.179">er</span> <span begin="21.224" end="21.531">go</span> <span begin="21.531" end="21.714">a</span><span begin="21.714" end="22.227">lone</span> <span begin="22.490" end="22.582">and</span> <span begin="22.582" end="22.705">I</span> <span begin="22.705" end="22.914">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="22.914" end="23.204">seem</span> <span begin="23.204" end="23.467">bro</span><span begin="23.467" end="23.700">ken</span><span begin="23.700" end="24.012">heart</span><span begin="24.012" end="24.215">ed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我从不孤身一人前往 也未流露出心碎的模样</span></p><p begin="24.406" end="28.152" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin