egin="34.125" end="34.624">night</span> <span begin="34.624" end="34.868">in</span> <span begin="34.868" end="35.071">the</span> <span begin="35.071" end="35.567">ho</span><span begin="35.567" end="36.190">tel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为他们不知道在酒店的那个夜晚</span></p><p begin="36.598" end="40.055" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="36.598" end="36.850">They</span> <span begin="36.850" end="37.093">weren&apos;t</span> <span begin="37.093" end="37.398">rid</span><span begin="37.398" end="37.606">ing</span> <span begin="37.606" end="37.837">in</span> <span begin="37.837" end="38.085">the</span> <span begin="38.085" end="38.592">car</span> <span begin="38.592" end="38.850">when</span> <span begin="38.850" end="39.074">we</span> <span begin="39.074" end="39.451">bo</span><span begin="39.451" end="39.581">th</span> <span begin="39.581" end="40.055">fell</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当我们双双坠入爱河 他们不在车里</span></p><p begin="40.302" end="44.058" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="40.302" end="40.433">Did</span><span begin="40.433" end="40.545">n&apos;t</span> <span begin="40.545" end="40.783">read</span> <span begin="40.820" end="41.062">the</span> <span begin="41.062" end="41.541">note</span> <span begin="41.541" end="41.810">on</span> <span begin="41.810" end="41.989">the</span> <span begin="42.044" end="42.294">Po</span><span begin="42.294" end="42.932">laroid</span> <span begin="43.020" end="43.481">pic</span><span begin="43.481" end="44.058">ture</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">没看到宝丽来照片上的留言</span></p><p begin="44.536" end="48.376" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="44.536" end="44.802">They</span> <span begin="44.802" end="45.025">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="45.025" end="45.319">know</span> <span begin="45.517" end="46.017">how</span> <span begin="46.017" end="46.381">mu</span><span begin="46.381" end="46.488">ch</span> <span begin="46.488" end="46.962">I</span> <span begin="46.995" end="47.552">miss</span> <span begin="47.552" end="48.376">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">他们不知道我对你的思念有多深</span></p><p begin="48.484" end="51.954" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="48.484" end="49.015">I</span> <span begin="49.015" end="49.419">wish</span> <span begin="49.471" end="50.340">I</span> <span begin="50.706" end="50.944">could</span> <span begin="50.944" end="51.094">f</span><span begin="51.094" end="51.954">ly</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我希望我能飞翔</span></p><p begin="52.182" end="55.925" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="52.182" end="52.330">I&apos;</span><span begin="52.330" end="52.459">d</span> <span begin="52.459" end="52.663">pick</span> <span begin="52.694" end="52.966">you</span> <span begin="52.966" end="53.176">up</span> <span begin="53.217" end="53.467">and</span> <span begin="53.467" end="53.665">we&apos;d</span> <span begin="53.712" end="53.965">go</span> <span begin="53.965" end="54.324">ba</span><span begin="54.324" end="54.468">ck</span> <span begin="54.468" end="54.879">in</span> <span begin="54.879" end="55.925">time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我会接上你 一起回到过去的时光</span></p><p begin="56.389" end="59.913" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="56.389" end="56.755">I&apos;</span><span begin="56.755" end="56.931">d</span> <span begin="56.931" end="57.293">write</span> <span begin="57.406" end="58.028">thi</span><span begin="58.028" end="58.212">s</span> <span begin="58.430" end="58.662">in</span> <span begin="58.662" end="58.785">the</span> <span begin="58.785" end="58.924">s</span><span begin="58.924" end="59.913">ky</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我会在天空中写下这句话</span></p><p begin="1:00.116" end="1:03.887" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:00.116" end="1:00.391">I</span> <span begin="1:00.391" end="1:00.625">miss</span> <span begin="1:00.625" end="1:00.872">you</span> <span begin="1:00.872" end="1:0